Name: Average time from Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER to Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time spent in Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR across all process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time between Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE and Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR in variants that include both activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average duration of Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR when it is immediately followed by Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average duration of Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR when it is immediately followed by Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by PRE_APPROVER and Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR in cases that eventually lead to Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR in cases that end in rejection loops
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time it takes Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR after the execution of Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time it takes Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR after the execution of Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to the Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR after Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to the Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR after Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Request Payment in successful variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time for Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR in variants where the budget owner and supervisor are the same person
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the next activity, grouped by whether the next activity is an approval or a rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
